4
00:00:22,589 --> 00:00:28,618
I listen to the audiobook at twice the speed
while I look at the book and follow along.

5
00:00:28,618 --> 00:00:31,809
And there are so many great things about that...
First of all,

6
00:00:31,809 --> 00:00:34,979
