11
00:00:51,158 --> 00:00:53,658
Another possibly even more important benefit
is that

12
00:00:53,658 --> 00:00:57,039
it keeps you in a straight line and keeps
you going.

13
00:00:57,039 --> 00:01:01,469
So you're not going back and rereading things,
you're not taking all kinds of unnecessary

14
00:01:01,469 --> 00:01:04,798
