point,
and this is absolutely one of the best

18
00:01:14,170 --> 00:01:17,310
and the most effective and effecient ways
to read.

19
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:20,250
You can take a book like The Richest Man in
Babylon

20
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:24,459
